<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0869004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0869004">一＝二【元】</note>
<note n="0869005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0869005">囉＝羅【三】</note>
<note n="0869006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0869006">欲＝飲【宋】</note>
<note n="0870001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0870001">皆＝廣【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0870002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0870002">Namaḥ sarva-buddhānāmapratihataśāsanānām, tadyathā Oṁ gagane gaganna-gañje ānaya sarvaṁ lahu lahu samaya-māusmara ākarṣaṇi mā vilamba yathepṣitaṁ me sampādaya svāhā.</note>
<note n="0870003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0870003">志＝至【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0871001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871001">妙香華 Saugandhika.</note>
<note n="0871002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871002">Plakṣa.</note>
<note n="0871003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871003">Udumbara.</note>
<note n="0871004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871004">Vaṭa.</note>
<note n="0871005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871005">Āmra.</note>
<note n="0871006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871006">Śirīṣa.</note>
<note n="0871007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871007">菩提樹 Bodhi-vṛkṣa.</note>
<note n="0871008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871008">瑠＝琉【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0871009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871009">Namaḥ sarva-buddhānāmapratihata śāsanānām, tadyathā Oṁ sarva-kilviṣanāśani, nāśaya sarva-duṣṭa-prayuktāṁ samaya-manusmara hūṁ jaḥ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0871010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871010">努＝拏【三】</note>
<note n="0871011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871011">刻＝剋【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0871012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871012">十地經 Ārya-daśa-bhumaka.</note>
<note n="0871013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871013">孔雀王經 Ārya-makā-mayūrī.</note>
<note n="0871014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871014">寶幢陀羅尼 Ārya-ratna-ketu-dhāriṇī.</note>
<note n="0871015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871015">辰＝晨【明】</note>
<note n="0871016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871016">於＋（於）【宋】</note>
<note n="0871017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871017">Namaḥ samantābuddhānām apratihata śāsanānām, tadyathā Oṁ saduṣṭāṁ-stambhaya hūṁ indīvara-dhāriṇe kumāra-krīḍa-rūpa-dhāriṇe bandha bandha samaya-manusmara sphaṭ sphaṭ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0871018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871018">Gomaya.</note>
<note n="0871019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871019">Māndārava.</note>
<note n="0871020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0871020">Indīvara.</note>
<note n="0872001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0872001">遍＝偏【宋】</note>
<note n="0872002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0872002">涕＝洟【三】</note>
</p>
